claim.claim-text:
19. A measurement method using a multiple-transit-echo wave, comprising:
receiving a target at a receptor disposed on a sensing area of a piezoelectric substrate of a SAW sensor system such that the target contacts the sensing area
converting a first electrical signal into a SAW;
sensing the target using the SAW;
outputting a SAW corresponding to the sensed target;
converting the SAW corresponding to the target into a second electrical signal; and
detecting a change in the second electrical signal by time-gating the multiple-transit-echo wave.
